quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  2,83,Min Й“amii fodoore e Й“iЙ“Й“e Isra'iil taa ndewee sonaa Alla moЖҙЖҙon e jibnaaЙ“e e jiidaaЙ“e e waayЙ—uЙ“e e waasЙ“e oЙ—on kaalana yimЙ“e Й“e ko moЖҙЖҙi darnon juulde tottiron asakal Й“aawo Й—uum cali-Й—on Й—uurni-Й—on sonaa seeЙ—a e mooЙ—on
  2,84,Nde Min Жҙetti fodoore mon wota on nduf ЖҙiiЖҙe mon taa on njaltin ko'e mon galleeji mon Й—i ndeen njaЙ“-Й—on ceediЙ—on Й—um
  2,85,"Rewi heen onon Й“ee oЙ—on mbara ko'e mon oЙ—on njaltina yimЙ“e e mon galleeji maЙ“Й“e, oЙ—on peГұГұina tooГұe mon e maЙ“Й“e, si Й“e arii e mon dahaaЙ“e coodtidonЙ“e yaltingol Й“e na harmi e mon, mbela on goonЙ—inat yoga e deftere nde njeddon yoga heen kala e mon waЙ—ooЙ“e Й—um njoЙ“di maЙ“Й“e ko koyeera weejo aduna Гұande darnga Й“e nduttee e lette Й“urЙ—e bonde Alla noon yeebotaako ko ngolloton ko"
  2,86,ЖҒeen soodirЙ“e laakara nguurndam aduna Й“e koynantaake lette Й“e keЙ“ataa ballo